@startuml 24-smart-stacks
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Smart Stacks (View and Open)

actor User
participant "HomePage" as UI
participant "GET /api/stacks" as API
participant "MemoryCache" as CACHE
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "contacts + embeddings" as DB
participant "SearchResultsPage" as SR

User -> UI: load home
UI -> API: GET /api/stacks
API -> CTX: stack defs for me
CTX -> DB: SELECT
DB --> CTX: rows
loop per stack
    API -> CACHE: get count(userId, stackId)
    alt hit
        CACHE --> API: count
    else miss
        API -> CTX: count by kind\n(tag filter / semantic query / classifier)
        CTX -> DB: SELECT / vector search
        DB --> CTX: n
        API -> CACHE: set 5min
    end
end
API --> UI: StackDto[] (exclude count=0)
UI --> User: scrollable stack cards

User -> UI: tap "AI founders"
UI -> SR: navigate /search?stackId=...
SR -> API: GET /api/stacks/:id/contacts
API --> SR: { contacts, nextPage }
SR --> User: filtered list with query chip

@enduml
